item.title: Mastering the Art of Coding with LeetCode: The Quest for the Coveted T-Shirt
item.author: Sandeep Undrakonda
item.description: T-Shirt The LeetCode T-Shirt: A Journey of Patience, Dedication, and Perseverance Introduction: In the world of coding, there is a special T-shirt that is coveted by programmers everywhere. It’s not a designer brand, nor is it particularly stylish. But it is a symbol of something greater. This T-shirt is from LeetCode, a popular platform for coding challenges, and it is not something you can just swipe your card and buy at the store.
